column9: SciDB is a massively parallel DBMS and complex analytics platform. It was conceived and designed to support very large scale quantitative analytics on images, time-series, numerical data and "whole graph" analytics in problem domains like bio-informatics, financial analytics, industrial and scientific sensor networks, and social network applications.
